MGIC Investment Corp. (MTG) , the mortgage
insurer that raised more than $1 billion this year selling stock
and debt, said Daniel Arrigoni has joined the board of directors
and will be on the audit and risk-management committees.  Arrigoni previously led the mortgage unit at U.S. Bancorp.,
Milwaukee-based MGIC said today in a statement distributed by PR
Newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
